<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/1437173-was-your-impression-that-jay-was-in-fact">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Was your impression that Jay was in fact drunk when he crashed? Mary thinks of it but won't ask Andrew. A kid on the way to school says his dad said Jay was drunk, but probably wasn't in the paper, so just rumor. But the paper may have said the car crushed him which another boy brought up. If it did then everything Andrew said is in question. No one seemed to notice he was crushed at the funeral. Was Jay drunk??? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
